<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintPointDistance.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] [[Assembly3_ConstraintPointDistance|Point distance]]: Add a "Point distance" to constrain the distance of two points in 2D or 3D.
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintEqualAngle.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] [[Assembly3_ConstraintEqualAngle|Equal angle]]: Add an "Equal angle" to equate the angles between two lines or normals. 
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintPointsSymmetric.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] [[Assembly3_ConstraintPointsSymmetric|Points symmetric]]: Add a "Points symmetric" constraint to make two points symmetric about a plane.
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintGeneral.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] () [[Assembly3_ConstraintSymmetricHorizontal|Symmetric horizontal]]: Symmetric horizontal
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintGeneral.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] () [[Assembly3_ConstraintSymmetricVertical|Symmetric vertical]]: Symmetric vertical 
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintSymmetricLine.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] [[Assembly3_ConstraintSymmetricLine|Symmetric line]]: Add a "Symmetric line" constraint to make two points symmetric about a line.
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintPointsHorizontal.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] [[Assembly3_ConstraintPointsHorizontal|Points horizontal]]: Add a "Points horizontal" constraint to make two points horizontal with each other when projected onto a plane.
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintPointsVertical.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] [[Assembly3_ConstraintPointsVertical|Points vertical]]: Add a "Points vertical" constraint to make two points vertical with each other when projected onto a plane.
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintLineHorizontal.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] [[Assembly3_ConstraintLineHorizontal|Line horizontal]]:Add a "Line horizontal" constraint to make a line segment horizontal when projected onto a plane.
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintLineVertical.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] [[Assembly3_ConstraintLineVertical|Line vertical]]: Add a "Line vertical" constraint to make a line segment vertical when projected onto a plane.
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintArcLineTangent.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] [[Assembly3_ConstraintArcLineTangent|Arc line tangent]]: Add an "Arc line tangent" constraint to make a line tangent to an arc at the start or end point of the arc.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintSketchPlane.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] [[Assembly3_ConstraintSketchPlane|Sketch plane]]: Add a "Sketch plane" to define the work plane of any draft element inside or following this constraint. 
:*: Add an empty "Sketch plane" to undefine the previous work plane.
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintLineLength.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] [[Assembly3_ConstraintLineLength|Line length]]: Add a "Line length" constrain the length of a non-subdivided Draft.Wire.
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintEqualLength.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] [[Assembly3_ConstraintEqualLength|Equal length]]: Add an "Equal length" constraint to make two lines of the same length.
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintLengthRatio.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] [[Assembly3_ConstraintLengthRatio|Length ratio]]: Add a "Length ratio" to constrain the length ratio of two lines. 
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintLengthDifference.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] [[Assembly3_ConstraintLengthDifference|Length difference]]: Add a "Length difference" to constrain the length difference of two lines.
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintLengthEqualPointLineDistance.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] [[Assembly3_ConstraintLengthEqualPointLineDistance|Length Equal Point Line Distance]]: Add a "Length Equal Point Line Distance" to constrain the distance 
:*: between a point and a line to be the same as the length of a another line.
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintGeneral.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] ( [[Image:Assembly ConstraintEqualLineArcLength.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] )[[Assembly3_ConstraintEqualLineArcLength|Equal Line Arc Length]]: Add an "Equal Line Arc Length" constraint to make a line of the same length as an arc.
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintMidPoint.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] [[Assembly3_ConstraintMidPoint|Mid point]]: Add a "Mid point" to constrain a point to the middle point of a line.
:* [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintDiameter.svg‚Äé‚Äé|32px]] [[Assembly3_ConstraintDiameter|Diameter]]: Add a "Diameter" to constrain the diameter of a circle/arc.
